articles.title: Tech stocks drag on S&P 500, Nasdaq after inflation data - Reuters
articles.description: The S&P 500 and the Nasdaq edged lower on Wednesday, weighed by a decline in technology stocks, while investors focused on the Federal Reserve's next move following an in-line inflation reading.
